.DT
cols
Discworld player help
cols

Name
.SI 5
cols - Set the number of columns on your screen.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
cols [number]
.EI

Describe
.SP 5 5
Cols is used to set the number of columns on the screen that you are using to
play the mud.  The default is 79 and if try to set it to anything that is not a
valid value, it will be set to this default.  Cols on its own will show
the current value.
.EP

Examples
.SI 5
cols
cols 132
cols 165
cols 79
.EI

See also
.SI 5
rows
.EI
